Validate must reject duplicate spec IDs, duplicate marker IDs, duplicate links, links referencing unknown specs or markers, resolution entries referencing unknown specs, unknown markers, unlinked edges, or duplicate resolution entries. It must also reject refs referencing unknown specs, duplicate refs, self-refs, directed cycles in the ref graph, ref resolutions referencing unknown specs, ref resolutions on spec pairs with no declared ref edge, or duplicate ref resolutions. Validation must pass when all references are consistent. See principles.specs_are_truth.